OL,3,CLord Ming Campbell, former Lib Dem
OL,4,Cleader, has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FThe former leader of the Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats, Menzies (Ming) Campbell,
OL,8,FLord Campbell of Pittenweem has died
OL,9,Fat the age of 84.
OL,11,FHis death was announced by his
OL,12,Fgrandson Gregor Grant-Suttie, who said
OL,13,Fexpressed "deepest sadness" at the
OL,14,Fpassing of his "beloved grandfather"
OL,15,Fand wrote: "Ming achieved a lot
OL,16,Fthrough his life, across sport, law
OL,17,Fand politics.
OL,26,@wD@LOU
