OL,6,F"But the myriad of accolades and
OL,7,Fawards he collected in his
OL,8,Fprofessional life paled in comparison
OL,9,Fto his achievements as a husband,
OL,10,Ffather figure, grandfather, and friend.
OL,12,F"He was a rare breed of Scotsman whose
OL,13,Fcontribution and ideas spanned so much
OL,14,Ffurther than his home country's
OL,15,Fborders; his level of thinking around
OL,16,Fissues that were international,
OL,17,Fparticularly around defence, gave
OL,18,FScotland the ability to be extremely
OL,19,Fproud of one of their own, whose ideas
OL,20,Fwere so much larger than narrowly
OL,21,Ffocused UK politics.
