OL,6,F"He was of a generation where hard
OL,7,Fwork and improving oneself through
OL,8,Feducation were prioritised, while the
OL,9,Fmodern-day notion of relative
OL,10,Fstandards versus others was alien to
OL,11,Fhim - in every step of his life he
OL,12,Fonly ever compared himself against his
OL,13,Fown exceptionally high standards."
OL,15,FThe former MP for North East Fife died
OL,16,Fin London after a period of respite
OL,17,Fcare.
