OL,6,FPrior to a career in politics,
OL,7,FCampbell was a keen sportsman,
OL,8,Fcompeting in 100 and 200m sprints and
OL,9,Fgoing on to represent Great Britain at
OL,10,Fthe 1964 Tokyo Olympics.
OL,12,FLiberal Democrat Leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,13,Fsaid of his predecessor: "With a
OL,14,Fparliamentary career spanning five
OL,15,Fdecades, Ming Campbell was a dedicated
OL,16,Fpublic servant, a tireless champion
OL,17,Ffor Fife, St Andrews and the UK, and a
OL,18,Ftrue Liberal giant.
OL,26,@uD@ZOU
