OL,3,CLord Ming Campbell, former Lib Dem
OL,4,Cleader, has died at the age of 84
OL,6,F"He was the Liberal Democrat
OL,7,Fspokesperson on foreign affairs when
OL,8,Fthe world changed on 9/11, and his
OL,9,Fprincipled leadership opposing the
OL,10,FIraq War was a mark of his morality,
OL,11,Fcourage and wisdom. He spoke up for
OL,12,Fwhat was right, even when it was hard.
OL,14,F"Like so many of us, I benefitted
OL,15,Fgreatly from Ming's advice and
OL,16,Fguidance over the many years we worked
OL,17,Fclosely together. But more than that,
OL,18,Fhe was an incredibly warm and caring
OL,19,Ffriend and colleague, with such
OL,20,Fgenerosity and humour.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
