OL,3,CLord Ming Campbell, former Lib Dem
OL,4,Cleader, has died at the age of 84
OL,6,F"Ming was always great company -
OL,7,Fwhether talking about sport with the
OL,8,Fauthority of a captain of Britain's
OL,9,Fathletics team and a British 100m
OL,10,Frecord-holder, or asking about you and
OL,11,Fyour family, when he would always pass
OL,12,Fon kind thoughts from his wife,
OL,13,FElspeth - his rock.
OL,15,F"All of us in the Liberal Democrat
OL,16,Ffamily and beyond will miss him
OL,17,Fterribly. Our thoughts are with all
OL,18,Fwho loved him."
